ActSocial Sciences and Humanities Research Council Act
PrecisReappointment of JACK MAURICE MINTZ of Calgary, Alberta, as a member of the Social Sciences and Humanities Research Council, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective September 29, 2014; and approval of the re-election by the Social Sciences and Humanities Research Council of JACK MAURICE MINTZ as Vice-President of the Social Sciences and Humanities Research Council.
